"http://html.hanspub.org/file/7-2580257x40_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>同理，假设主要靠资本获得收入的居民人数为M，资本总收入为F，个人资本收入为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/7-2580257x41_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的相格数为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/7-2580257x42_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，人数为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/7-2580257x43_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，资本收入分布系统的微观态数为：</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.21110-formula314"><label>(1-13)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/7-2580257x44_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>其控制条件为：</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/7-2580257x45_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>和<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/7-2580257x46_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula> (1-14)</p><p>对<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/7-2580257x47_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>引入参量<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/7-2580257x48_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>、对<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/7-2580257x49_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>引入参量<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/7-2580257x50_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，可得资本收入分布系统的最可几分布：</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.21110-formula315"><label>(1-15)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/7-2580257x51_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>收入处于区间<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/7-2580257x52_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的相